          <ThingDef ParentName="MPBFPM_BaseHumanMakeableGun" Name="QM_Gun_CarnagePistol_Bond" Abstract="True">
            <label>persona Cerberus Tactical Pistol</label>
            <description>The Cerberus pattern pistol is product of Realware&#8482; industries compact design and cutting-edge ballistics. This pattern of pistol is famed for it's both reliablility and lethality in battlefield. It is favored by operatives across the corporations whose still enjoys smell of gunpowder.\n\n"Because in an capitalist utopia, the invisible hand is trigger happy" said the veteran merc\n\nThis weapon has an onboard persona that can bond to only a single person. The wielder and intelligent weapon can synchronize their reflexes and attack with frightening speed, accuracy, and creativity. Once bonded to a wielder, the weapon's persona will refuse to be wielded by anyone else.</description>
            <techLevel>Spacer</techLevel>
            <graphicData>
              <texPath>Things/WeaponRanged/Cerberus</texPath>
              <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
            </graphicData>
            <soundInteract>Interact_SMG</soundInteract>
            <weaponTags>
              <li>RealWareSideArm</li>
            </weaponTags>
            <statBases>
              <Mass>3</Mass>
              <AccuracyTouch>0.968</AccuracyTouch>
              <AccuracyShort>0.968</AccuracyShort>
              <AccuracyMedium>0.484</AccuracyMedium>
              <AccuracyLong>0.181</AccuracyLong>
              <RangedWeapon_Cooldown>0.361</RangedWeapon_Cooldown>
            </statBases>
            <verbs>
              <li>
                <verbClass>Verb_Shoot</verbClass>
                <hasStandardCommand>true</hasStandardCommand>
                <defaultProjectile>Bullet_CarnagePistol_Bond</defaultProjectile>
                <warmupTime>0.5</warmupTime>
                <range>22.9</range>
                <burstShotCount>2</burstShotCount>
                <ticksBetweenBurstShots>3</ticksBetweenBurstShots>
                <soundCast>Shot_MachinePistol</soundCast>
                <soundCastTail>GunTail_Light</soundCastTail>
                <muzzleFlashScale>9</muzzleFlashScale>
              </li>
            </verbs>
            <tools>
              <li>
                <label>grip</label>
                <capacities>
                  <li>Blunt</li>
                </capacities>
                <power>9.75</power>
                <cooldownTime>1.7</cooldownTime>
              </li>
              <li>
                <label>barrel</label>
                <capacities>
                  <li>Blunt</li>
                  <li>Poke</li>
                </capacities>
                <power>9.75</power>
                <cooldownTime>1.7</cooldownTime>
              </li>
            </tools>
          </ThingDef>
          <ThingDef ParentName="MPBFPM_BaseHumanMakeableGun" Name="QM_Gun_RetributionAssaultRifle_Bond" Abstract="True">
            <label>persona Retribution Assault Rifle</label>
            <description>The Retribution Pattern assault rifle serves as an emblem of prowess and showcase of unparalleled ballistic precision of Realware&#8482; industry. \n\n"In a world where the market dictates the rules of engagement, this rifle guarentees a yield" said the savvy merc\n\nThis weapon has an onboard persona that can bond to only a single person. The wielder and intelligent weapon can synchronize their reflexes and attack with frightening speed, accuracy, and creativity. Once bonded to a wielder, the weapon's persona will refuse to be wielded by anyone else.</description>
            <techLevel>Spacer</techLevel>
            <graphicData>
              <texPath>Things/WeaponRanged/Retribution</texPath>
              <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
            </graphicData>
            <equippedAngleOffset>45</equippedAngleOffset>
            <soundInteract>Interact_Rifle</soundInteract>
            <weaponTags>
              <li>RealWareMainArm</li>
            </weaponTags>
            <statBases>
              <Mass>4</Mass>
              <AccuracyTouch>0.665</AccuracyTouch>
              <AccuracyShort>0.968</AccuracyShort>
              <AccuracyMedium>0.907</AccuracyMedium>
              <AccuracyLong>0.303</AccuracyLong>
              <RangedWeapon_Cooldown>1.084</RangedWeapon_Cooldown>
            </statBases>
            <verbs>
              <li>
                <verbClass>Verb_Shoot</verbClass>
                <hasStandardCommand>true</hasStandardCommand>
                <defaultProjectile>Bullet_RetributionAssaultRifle_Bond</defaultProjectile>
                <warmupTime>0.5</warmupTime>
                <range>30.9</range>
                <burstShotCount>3</burstShotCount>
                <ticksBetweenBurstShots>5</ticksBetweenBurstShots>
                <soundCast>Shot_Autocannon</soundCast>
                <soundCastTail>GunTail_Medium</soundCastTail>
                <muzzleFlashScale>9</muzzleFlashScale>
              </li>
            </verbs>
            <tools>
              <li>
                <label>stock</label>
                <capacities>
                  <li>Blunt</li>
                </capacities>
                <power>9.75</power>
                <cooldownTime>1.7</cooldownTime>
              </li>
              <li>
                <label>barrel</label>
                <capacities>
                  <li>Blunt</li>
                  <li>Poke</li>
                </capacities>
                <power>9.75</power>
                <cooldownTime>1.7</cooldownTime>
              </li>
            </tools>
          </ThingDef>
          <ThingDef ParentName="MPBFPM_Bullet" Name="Bullet_CarnagePistol_Bond" Abstract="True">
            <label>Cerberus bullet</label>
            <projectile>
              <damageDef>Bullet</damageDef>
              <damageAmountBase>22</damageAmountBase>
              <stoppingPower>0.5</stoppingPower>
              <speed>80</speed>
            </projectile>
            <graphicData>
              <texPath>Things/Projectile/Bullet_small</texPath>
            </graphicData>
          </ThingDef>
          <ThingDef ParentName="MPBFPM_Bullet" Name="Bullet_RetributionAssaultRifle_Bond" Abstract="True">
            <label>Retribution bullet</label>
            <projectile>
              <damageDef>Bullet</damageDef>
              <damageAmountBase>27</damageAmountBase>
              <stoppingPower>1</stoppingPower>
              <armorPenetrationBase>0.28</armorPenetrationBase>
              <speed>80</speed>
            </projectile>
            <weaponTags Inherit="False" />
            <graphicData>
              <texPath>Things/Projectile/Bullet_big</texPath>
            </graphicData>
          </ThingDef>
        </value>
